State Regulations

Subdivision 4 of section
382-b
of the

Executive Law directs local governments to provide for enforcement of section
382-b
of the

Executive Law. Enforcement of section
382-b
of the

Executive Law shall include, but shall not be limited to, enforcement of the
provisions of this Part. Notes
